1337632801.text: "Flavopiridol, a pan-CDK inhibitor and targeting CDK2, CDK4, CDK6 and CDK9, synergizes with sorafenib to induce cytotoxicity and potentiate antitumorigenic activity in EGFR and HER -2 and mutant RAS and RAF breast cancer model systems XREF_BIBR."
